Package: beep
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Blaine Motsinger <blaine@renderorange.com>
Depends: sqlite3
Homepage: https://github.com/adventurehound/beep
Description: Lightweight, self-hosted web analytics tracker
 beep captures pageviews with no cookies and no personal data collection.
 It provides a REST API for querying stats and a CLI for management.
